.PP
Accepts color atoms (\fIred\fR, \fIblue\fR, \fIlight_green\fR, etc.) or index colors (0-255). Index 0-15 correspond to the named colors in \fIcolor_atom/0\fR.

.PP
Example:

.IP
.nf
1> io_ansi:underline_color(red).
<<"\\e[58;5;1m">>
2> io_ansi:underline_color(light_cyan).
<<"\\e[58;5;14m">>
3> io_ansi:underline_color(196).
<<"\\e[58;5;196m">>

.fi


